{"tid":851345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發展「合理」　落後專制窮國　出口器官賺錢　不也一種天然資源","createTime":"2018-10-07T05:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T05:43:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"405b6535f9a5b0884830f281758f136a6c81f2e8","tid":851345,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156585061787357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156585061787357&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a86f584d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156585061787357</a><br />\n<br />\n不過看起來也很正確, 未來的世界, 那些落後的專制窮國, 只要有完整的醫療設施, 就可以靠出口器官賺錢. 這不是變成一種天然資源?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKenny Bok:<br />\n不會。<br />\n質量太差，冇人會買次等貨。<br />\n<br />\n鄧卓文:<br />\n所以先係賣維人，因為相對上質量有保障d<br />\n<br />\nJames Chan:<br />\n咦？呢個咪西藏山區肺？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/DummyHistory/M.1313423667.A.E5E.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FDummyHistory%2FM.1313423667.A.E5E.html&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a9d77fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/DummyHistory/M.1313423667.A.E5E.html</a><br />\n<br />\n人類文明本來就建基於強姦.<br />\n我們每一個人的祖先都一定有強姦犯.<br />\n<br />\n而帝國就是強姦這件事的政治版.<br />\n既然是強姦, 被姦者當然不會有選擇的權利吧.<br />\n強姦就是弱肉強食.<br />\n<br />\n這跟甚麼文化傳統思想沒甚麼關係. 而是人類的文明是從力量上的弱<br />\n肉強食開始的. 人類本來就像狩獵的猛獸一樣, 喜歡的食物就搶, 喜<br />\n歡的異性就強姦, 喜歡殺就殺.<br />\n<br />\n後來人類變聰明了, 就產生了牧畜, 也就是與其去狩獵會跑的獵物,<br />\n不如讓獵物馴服下來, 活夠了就被吃. 而國家和統治關係的形成, 就<br />\n不過是牧畜這種技術的進化版, 既然人可以養豬養羊, 人類還不是一<br />\n樣是哺乳類動物, 所以也可以當成牲畜般去養.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/GNeziZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGNeziZ&h=7366a8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/sCrRa2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsCrRa2&h=1cda9dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/nXt8eC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnXt8eC&h=8c386d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/AqLs9T\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAqLs9T&h=f97705e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/a2WEQ2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fa2WEQ2&h=dc61fa99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1538736557.A.9B8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1538736557.A.9B8.html&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=1cb3c0ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1538736557.A.9B8.html</a><br />\n<br />\n　　或許中國廠商能將葉克膜硬體做得十分便宜，但是葉克膜使用需要照顧提供者大量專<br />\n　　業訓練，並不容易，過多的專業人力會造成活摘產業中很大的獲利損失，並且可能發<br />\n　　生非預期併發症，導致器官無法使用，商譽受損。隨意的逮捕與殺害成本反而更低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180921/1434289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434289%2F&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=17da5628\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434289%2F&h=0ce3caca\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180921/1434289/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國拐賣人口案件頻傳，一名劉姓少女幾年前出遊時被一名年約30歲的漂亮大姐姐拐走賣掉，所幸她急中生智，不僅成功逃脫、還以人民幣500元（約合新台幣2250元）的價格反手把漂亮大姐姐賣給一個70幾歲的老頭，最後漂亮大姐姐被數名不同男性性侵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180921/1434289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434289%2F&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=17da5628\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434289%2F&h=0ce3caca\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180921/1434289/</a><br />\n<br />\n竟傻傻相信了劉慧的話隨她回家，待在旅館房間裡等劉慧帶姊妹自投羅網，沒想到恢復自由的劉慧一人走在街上越想越氣，竟隨便找了一個老頭就把人口販子賣了，但回家後還是良心不安告知了父母，父母聽完嚇得趕緊報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方獲報詢線逮捕買走人口販子的老翁，老翁坦承他性侵完人口販子後又轉手以人民幣4000元（約合新台幣1.8萬元）的價格賣給了別人，最後人口販子雖被救出，但也被判處了無期徒刑"},{"pid":"012ce111af837da9774dc4e1bfdbf5c7ccf0e987","tid":851345,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"可持續發展<br />\nrenewable resources<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}